Jericho Scott, 16, was shot dead in New Haven, Connecticut on Sunday .
He was the star pitcher for Will Power Fitness team in the Youth Baseball League of New Haven in 2009 when he was banned from the team because he threw 40mph .
The budding star had five no-hitters in the team's first eight games of the season before being told he had to sit out the game .
Scott was shot in the shoulder, hand and wrist but is in stable condition .